img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  迪迪仔就睇佢會唔會去蛆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}